                                <note type="palaeographic" xml:lang="en">
                                    <p>Right-to-left direction, horizontal alignment, vertical module, irregular <term xml:lang="la">ductus</term>, triangular interpunction, centered layout.</p>
                                    
                                    <p><g type="pl">D</g> wide, with square module;</p>
                                    
                                    <p><g type="pl">M</g> composed of four oblique strokes;</p>
                                    
