    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="Latin">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName ref="#honoratus">Turranius Hono<unclear>r</unclear>atus</persName>
                    <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>eliae</ex></expan> Iovinae, dulcissimae <choice><reg>compari</reg><orig>conpari</orig></choice>
                    <lb n="3"/>quae vixit mecum annos <num value="10">X</num>, menses <num value="2">II</num>.
                    <lb n="4"/>Si quis <choice><reg>eam</reg><orig>ean</orig></choice> <supplied reason="omitted">arcam</supplied> voluerit aper<choice><corr>i</corr><sic>e</sic></choice>re
                    <lb n="5"/>dabit fisco <measure type="fine" unit="roman_pound" commodity="silver" quantity="5">argenti pondo
                    <lb n="6"/>quinque</measure>
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app></app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p><persName ref="#honoratus" xml:lang="la">Turranius Honoratus</persName>, to <persName ref="#iovina" xml:lang="la">Aurelia Iovina</persName>, sweetest companion, who lived with me 10 years and 2 months.</p>
                
                <p>If anyone wishes to open this sarcophagus, he shall pay to the treasury five (roman) pounds of silver.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                <p><persName ref="#honoratus">Turranio Onorato</persName>, ad <persName ref="#iovina">Aurelia Iovina</persName>, dolcissima compagna, che visse con me 10 anni e 2 mesi.</p>
                
                <p>Se qualcuno vorrà aprire questa arca, verserà al fisco cinque libbre (romane) d'argento.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en">
                <p>The <term xml:lang="la">gens</term> <persName xml:lang="la">Turrania</persName> is abundantly documented in Concordia, including in this very necropolis <ref target="./fabianus.xml">(<term xml:lang="la">CIL</term> V 8692)</ref>.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="it">
                <p>La <term xml:lang="la">gens</term> <persName xml:lang="la">Turrania</persName> è molto attestata in Concordia anche nella stessa necropoli <ref target="./fabianus.xml">(<term xml:lang="la">CIL</term> V 8692)</ref>.</p></div>
